fm: int arrayNesting(vector<int> &nums) {         int maxLen = 0, i = 0, numMinus = 0, size = nums.size();         for(int i = 0 ; i < size;++i) {             if(nums[i] != -1) {                 int len = 0, j = i;                 while (nums[j] != -1) {                     int temp = nums[j];                     nums[j] = -1;                     j = temp;                     ++len;                     ++numMinus;                 }                 maxLen = max(maxLen, len);             }         }         return maxLen;     }

fm: vector<vector<int>> matrixReshape(vector<vector<int>> &nums, int r, int c) {         int n = nums.size();         if (n == 0)             return nums;         int m = nums[0].size();         if (n * m != r * c)             return nums;         vector<vector<int>> matrix;         vector<int> temp;         int x = 0, y = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             for (int j = 0; j < m; ++j) {                 temp.push_back(nums[i][j]);                 ++y;                 if (y == c) {                     ++x;                     y = 0;                     matrix.push_back(temp);                     temp.clear();                 }             }         }         return matrix;     }
